<p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C7CD5AF8" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C7CD5AF8">H-1 Bullying Form</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px">This form is used to report conduct which may violate Policy 4103, Harassment, Intimidation, and Bullying. Form H-1 must be completed by the complainant or school personnel.</span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C6C85AFB" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C6C85AFB">2017 - 2018 School Board Effectiveness </a></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align:left"><br></p>
<p style="text-align:left"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1CC5EFC" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1CC5EFC">2019 - 2020 Policy Guide</a></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align:left"><br></p>
<p><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1C95FFC" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1C95FFC"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px">Harrison County Schools 5-Year Plan</span></span></a></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C2CB5EFF" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C2CB5EFF">School Entry Health Requirements Pre-K</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif">All children entering an approved pre-kindergarten (“Pre-K”) classroom must have age-appropriate immunizations1 upon enrollment as mandated by state law.</span></span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/22C5CF5E" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/22C5CF5E">School Entry Health Requirements K-12</a></span></span></p>
<div title="Page 1"><div><div><div><p><span style="font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif">State law and rules require that all children entering school in West Virginia for the first time in grades K-12 must show proof of immunization against diphtheria, pertussis, tetanus, polio, measles, mumps, rubella, varicella, and hepatitis B unless properly medically exempted.</span></span></p></div></div></div></div>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px"><a data-cke-saved-href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1CE5EFE" href="http://www.harcoboe.net/file/28C1CE5EFE">2019-20 Preliminary Budget</a></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family:Georgia,serif"><span style="font-size:12px">This document provides highlights of the FY 20 budget (July 1, 2019, through June 30, 2020). Please note that throughout the budget document FY followed by the last two digits of the ending applicable year will reference the fiscal year. </span></span></p>
